# ===== Mitos workspace state (regenerated by the tool; not source) =====
.mitos/
live_axioms.md
*sync_snapshot.md
# Root-anchored: the repo root is a dogfood `mitos init` workspace, so `init`
# regenerates a workspace `format-spec.md` at root. The package copy is the only
# tracked C5 source (V1-D7). Leading slash is load-bearing — a bare `format-spec.md`
# would also ignore `mitos/format-spec.md` (the package data) and re-open the
# Phase-1a missing-from-wheel bug.
/format-spec.md

